# AI History

## 2026-02-19
- Standardized utility strategy around Go-first CLIs where appropriate.
- Added root Makefile orchestration for build/install/uninstall across utilities.
- Added uninstall support for each utility and documented root usage.
- Introduced Go `fmt-table` project (`utils/fmt-table`) as the preferred implementation.
- Kept `utils/fmt-table-py` available as a legacy reference.

## 2026-02-20
- Added Go `git-create-gist` utility wrapping `gh gist create`.
- Kept gist visibility private-by-default with explicit `--public` opt-in.
- Added description support and root Makefile integration for lifecycle targets.
